The violators shields quickly went down as the scorpion tank with Skywarp was 
launched off the trainer base. A door opened below the ship and the scorpion 
tank quickly entered as did Gemini 1 and two. Vile turns to Gemini 1 and 2 
and growls.

Vile: "Cyanide may be caught but now these fools will all be destroyed! 
Goodbye Cyanide you haved risked yourself for us all."

And with that Vile opened a small compartment at his control console and 
pressed it. Immeidately two Mega photon torpedoes, six photon torpedoes, four 
laser cannons, the four multi phase laser cannons, and both mega cannons, 
shooting 3 shots each opened fire on the triaer base followed by a massive 
blast fired at the base from the Vile cannon. As this happened Vile shook his 
head and began to walk away when the Violator was hammered by 8 massive 
blasts causing the ship to shake violently and throw Vile and Methos from 
where they were standing. Vile then got up and growls as Gemini 2 rushed to 
his console and brought up a visual of a massive portal, with an infecticon 
ship exiting it and hovering over the trainer base.

Vile: "Infecticons... prepare to open fire on that ship with everything we 
have."

On the Infecticon ship two black beings seemingly made of energy look at two 
orbs in front of them, one displaying Predacon and X-Predacon energy 
signatures as well as some unknown types. One orb begins to glow as in the 
center of the large dark control room a bright circle of light appears. As 
this happens, a column of light shines striaght down and into the trainer 
base(dont worry this isnt an attack) and engulfs cyanide,  who immediately 
goes into a panick.

Cyanide: "No they're here! Help! Help!"

As cyanide screams 8 rings appear around him before he himself turns into a 
being of light. Soon he dissapears with the rings forming a sort of bulge in 
the column which quickly speeds up the beam of light and into the Infecticon 
ship...

--part1_e1.15a92fd5.284e8c9c_boundary
